Package: TAPChunks
Type: Package
Title: A library of tools for accessing and manipulating chunks of telemetry data
Version: 0.2.3
Author: JTA
Maintainer: JTA <duarte.gomes@jtaweb.net>
Description: A library of tools for accessing and manipulating chunks.  
    This library contains simple functions that will allow the user to access
    and create data chunks from the Spiceworks telemetry.  
